  <string name="terms_dialog_title">Aurora Security Notice</string>
  <string name="terms_dialog_body">Aurora Security is a personal safety assistance tool only. It is not an emergency dispatch service, police reporting system, medical service, or guaranteed rescue solution.\n\nAlerts, recordings, AI analysis, SMS, phone calls, location sharing, and other features may fail, be delayed, or be inaccurate due to device limitations, permissions, network issues, operating system restrictions, or third-party service interruptions.\n\nYou are responsible for keeping permissions enabled, maintaining your emergency contacts, and testing the app regularly. If you are in immediate danger, contact official emergency services as soon as possible.\n\nBy tapping Agree, you acknowledge and accept these risks, confirm that you have had the opportunity to review the full Terms of Use, and agree to be bound by them.</string>
